This is a movie about every day life in Peru. People striving to survive. Corruption is everywhere rampant, but generosity sometimes is displayed unexpectedly.
There is not much of a plot ; it is sort of a fortnight in the life of an ordinary guy, during which his life takes some changes.
I enjoyed it. I like realistic movies.
